{"tid":636342,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"其實仲有冇人去HMV","createTime":"2018-04-20T18:15:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T12:36:13.000Z","uid":103357,"like":14,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"78c1f31cd002f47c4ef3eab6fb56c607f3eac1d8","tid":636342,"uid":103357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T18:15:21.000Z","msg":"見RSD 就諗起舊時HMV係真係一間唱片舖 啲staff係真係有一定音樂知識<br />\n依家又賣玩具 又賣熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似有手有腳就請咁 見到都唔撚想入去<br />\n好撚記得幾個月前喺尖沙咀 有個𡃁仔serve個大陸佬 條友唔記得咗套戲名 但係一形容吓個𡃁仔就即刻知係咩戲 導演名都講得出<br />\n之後我叫返佢幫我搵隻cd 仲推薦埋我同類型有乜好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住唔通咸魚翻生 講返啲有水準嘅人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌 點知再下次去 第二個𡃁仔serve我 乜柒都唔識 歌又唔知 人又唔知 最後激鳩氣走撚咗算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453323ace15d6781214bc0a9546e8a92e09097a9","tid":636342,"uid":93855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:58:47.000Z","msg":"冇計 淨賣cd難生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65678150254f622a8ebeb90fd7a1490eae5ab7e","tid":636342,"uid":42804,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T06:06:36.000Z","msg":"真正買碟已經唔多，願意買嘅都係歌迷為主。<br />\n但買開日韓嘅，一般都唔會去hmv，因為價錢比較貴，又唔夠信和以及網上訂購快。"},{"pid":"1b9a12cd2bb0ba230935a0bc086cd8a9382985c0","tid":636342,"uid":104446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T07:57:39.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"247aa5eefefe64a07fcf19df55105da12368d094","tid":636342,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T08:40:28.000Z","msg":"去行下噉囉<br />\n但真係冇咁多嘢買<br />\n唉，好懷念以前嘅HMV<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a29bfbdf383269fcffc33e377418917e6d5319","tid":636342,"uid":34789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T13:37:29.000Z","msg":"本地碟/港台版碟去CDWH<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日版碟上網買<br />\n<br />\nHMV貴d之餘太多垃雜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9189243fb3ec38be585aef4c9ab5bfe25630716","tid":636342,"uid":66178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T13:49:05.000Z","msg":"想問下大家買CD除咗上網,HMV同埋信和,仲有邊到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc341dcb0e5e84728ecb896dedfef2fcd5994b3","tid":636342,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9189243fb3ec38be585aef4c9ab5bfe25630716","tid":636342,"uid":66178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T13:49:05.000Z","msg":"想問下大家買CD除咗上網,HMV同埋信和,仲有邊到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T13:51:16.000Z","msg":"cd warehouse"},{"pid":"55c2522cb5b4a430b39746d854159ca99cdf8049","tid":636342,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T13:51:53.000Z","msg":"HMV 垃垃圾圾咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c757c22d3ab0e13abd0aeb68895d0a8f15f87db4","tid":636342,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9189243fb3ec38be585aef4c9ab5bfe25630716","tid":636342,"uid":66178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T13:49:05.000Z","msg":"想問下大家買CD除咗上網,HMV同埋信和,仲有邊到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T16:27:41.000Z","msg":"街鋪咪cd warehouse 節拍 香港唱片果d<br />\n網上咪去amazon 或者一d台灣網買<br />\n<br />\n連鎖鋪頭黎講 hmv最貴 不過d貨算齊<br />\n通常經過都會去行下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d241896fb8f074c1e6adff79e81c54da1e7212a8","tid":636342,"uid":183102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T17:02:20.000Z","msg":"有時有啲外國冷門啲嘅碟真係hmv先搵到<br />\n不過普遍都係賣得好貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時都係鐘意去cd warehouse 買，價錢合理好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6018f95d150a0c64d5466da92629e4997ce5af","tid":636342,"uid":103357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:45:55.000Z","msg":"日本碟要成十算真係當人on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過英文碟其實都叫合理價 貴出面少少真係唔係問題 而係俾貴你 我應該要有合理嘅服務掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n舊時啲staff你r下佢 就真係會同你傾吓電影傾吓音樂 而家好似叫你幫手check下嘢都攞佢命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁嘅服務態度同knowledge我真係情願去cdwh 平又平啲 又有金髮大波妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7ecca16a2ebd2a671a8f23a6c60c6081b11b26","tid":636342,"uid":26946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b6018f95d150a0c64d5466da92629e4997ce5af","tid":636342,"uid":103357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:45:55.000Z","msg":"日本碟要成十算真係當人on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過英文碟其實都叫合理價 貴出面少少真係唔係問題 而係俾貴你 我應該要有合理嘅服務掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n舊時啲staff你r下佢 就真係會同你傾吓電影傾吓音樂 而家好似叫你幫手check下嘢都攞佢命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁嘅服務態度同knowledge我真係情願去cdwh 平又平啲 又有金髮大波妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T12:36:13.000Z","msg":"我依家去hmv都係睇碟多<br />\n好認同你講,佢地賣日本碟價錢真係貴d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得佢地d職員成日都好似好忙咁,行黎行去又係d客隔離執碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過問職員野都係答唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  跟住行開左無搵其他人幫你<img src=\"/assets/faces/